%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Th%E1%BB%ABa-v%C4%83n-H%C3%A0-B%E1%BA%AFc-ch%C6%B0-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1o-ti%E1%BA%BFt-%C4%91%E1%BB%99-nh%E1%BA%ADp-tri%E1%BB%81u-hoan-h%E1%BB%89-kh%E1%BA%A9u-h%C3%A0o-tuy%E1%BB%87t-c%C3%BA-k%E1%BB%B3-08/poem-OiY9UJ2Bq-6yhQgPEQd2pQ">Thừa văn Hà Bắc chư đạo tiết độ nhập triều, hoan hỉ khẩu hào tuyệt cú kỳ 08 - 承聞河北諸道節度入朝歡喜口號絕句其八</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-xu%C3%A2n/poem-CFOxLxsUUkAoEyjRHh4nBA">Thương xuân - 傷春</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/author-l-NINz3JTJVTCX2aN0HlSQ">Thái Thuận</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-T%C3%B9ng/Trung-thu-%C4%91%E1%BB%91i-nguy%E1%BB%87t/poem-F4NWxWDTvtWpixhAlHo4QQ">Trung thu đối nguyệt - 中秋對月</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-T%C3%B9ng/author-GOwunwSP5NTeq-OyDkmY7g">Tào Tùng</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-V%C4%83n-L%C3%BD/V%E1%BB%8Dng-D%E1%BB%A5c-Thu%C3%BD-s%C6%A1n/poem-DWAT7z2Az3jZKO2Lmh6G2g">Vọng Dục Thuý sơn - 望浴翠山</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-V%C4%83n-L%C3%BD/author-25FyZ6rpi0e-evNzYaWVZQ">Nguyễn Văn Lý</a>)<br></div>	</div>
